law campaigning must end at noon friday 
although saturdays twohour session was not a debate the 
candidates moderators and journalists clashed frequently 
the questioning was supposed to alternate between the 
candidates but the number of inquiries for tyminski far 
outnumbered those for walesa 
neither candidate was very specific about his programs walesa 
said his positions were well known tyminski often clashed with 
